### Login as employee
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "loginId": "EMP001",
  "password": "emp123"
}

### Login as manager
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "loginId": "MGR001",
  "password": "manager123"
}

### Get employees
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employees

### Get employees under manager Rajesh
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employees/manager/1

### Create out duty gatepass as Amit
POST http://localhost:8080/api/gatepasses
Content-Type: application/json
X-Employee-Id: 4

{
  "gatepassType": "OUT_DUTY",
  "requestDate": "2026-04-20",
  "fromTime": "11:00:00",
  "toTime": "16:00:00",
  "outLocation": "Client Office",
  "reason": "Client visit"
}

### Create plant-to-plant gatepass as Priya
POST http://localhost:8080/api/gatepasses
Content-Type: application/json
X-Employee-Id: 5

{
  "gatepassType": "PLANT_TO_PLANT",
  "requestDate": "2026-04-20",
  "fromTime": "10:00:00",
  "toTime": "13:00:00",
  "fromPlantId": 1,
  "toPlantId": 2,
  "reason": "Maintenance coordination"
}

### Create half-day gatepass as Suresh
POST http://localhost:8080/api/gatepasses
Content-Type: application/json
X-Employee-Id: 6

{
  "gatepassType": "HALF_DAY",
  "requestDate": "2026-04-20",
  "fromTime": "14:00:00",
  "toTime": "18:00:00",
  "halfDaySession": "SECOND_HALF",
  "reason": "Personal work"
}

### Employee sees own requests
GET http://localhost:8080/api/gatepasses/my
X-Employee-Id: 4

### Manager sees pending approvals
GET http://localhost:8080/api/manager/gatepasses/pending
X-Manager-Id: 1

### Manager approves gatepass
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/manager/gatepasses/1/approve
Content-Type: application/json
X-Manager-Id: 1

{
  "remarks": "Approved"
}

### Manager rejects gatepass
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/manager/gatepasses/1/reject
Content-Type: application/json
X-Manager-Id: 1

{
  "remarks": "Rejected due to workload"
}

### HR sees all gatepasses
GET http://localhost:8080/api/hr/gatepasses

### HR sees gatepasses by date range
GET http://localhost:8080/api/hr/gatepasses?fromDate=2026-04-01&toDate=2026-04-30

### Security sees approved gatepasses
GET http://localhost:8080/api/security/gatepasses/approved

### Security checkout
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/security/gatepasses/1/checkout

### Security checkin
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/security/gatepasses/1/checkin
